 26/7/16 . Have been under a terribl bombard for three day now . Our trench has disappear and we are hold on in shell hole . Have advanc in front of his barrag and are better off here . Have no food or water . Do n't know where the Battalion is . Was buri by a shell yesterday Palmer dug me out . He is not with me now . 27/7/16 . Last night we were reliev by the 5th Brigad . Found my way back to Becourt Wood . I found Palmer there he has a slight wound in the head . The cook gave me a grand hot meal and I had a good sleep
